    "The number and fraction of valid, unique, and novel molecular designs are calculated for each model.",
    "For the designs, the mean and standard deviation of (1) the natural-product-likeness values 71, (2) the number of sp 3 carbons, (3) the number of aliphatic rings, (4) the number of spiro atoms, (5) molecular weight, (6) size of the largest fused ring system, (7) the number of heavy atoms and the corresponding Kolmogorov-Smirnov distance to the training and test sets (KStrain and KStest, respectively) are reported.",
